In Love and Sprockets, Taneka Stotts and Genue Revuelta take you to a world where robots are among us - and capable of love and sexiness.

In Don't Break Up The Party, the team is in the midst of their last D&D campaign, but the real drama is happening between Bea and Dell.

And in Purple Love Balloon, the young couple is hot on the hunt for their balloon - and a romantic adventure.

Plus, another installment of the DivorcÃ©e Club, a look behind the curtain of Purple Love Balloon, and more!

description: The tragicomic journey of Bizarro takes a dark turn. Guided by the Trickster, every attempt to do something good leads to something far, far worse. Can Superman and the Regime stop him before the scale of his destructive blunders leads to a major disaster?
